data.description:
Horse property, zoned agriculture. 
You can have any animal you want. 

Log home recently refinished exterior, if you don't like utility bills this is your home. 

With the 7.35kw solar array and geothermal HVAC your utilities are minimal throughout the year. Solar system and HVAC are paid for. 

LED bulbs throughout the house. 

Within walking distance to the river. 

Orchard with over 12 fruit trees. 

Fire pit, perfect for parties. 

Two auto start pellet stoves purchased in 2013, one upstairs one in the basement. 

New Water Softener, whole house water manifold, new Water Heater, reverse osmosis drinking water. 

New Fridge, new induction stovetop, double ovens for those who love to bake. 

Fenced backyard and pasture, large shade trees. 

Large covered trex deck patio added in 2013. 
Lifetime metal roof in 2013. 
New Windows and French doors 2015. 

Asphalt driveway and Garage built in 2013, garage is wired has two 240v outlets, has lots of storage in rafters and racks, fits full size extended can trucks. 

Multiple sheds on the property, for toys, tools or whatever. 

High speed internet access available. 

Radon Abatement System
data.whatILove: Orchard, fenced in pasture. Views, edible backyard with blackberries, raspberries, grapes and fruit trees. $9 electricity bills and $15 gas bills.
